  "synopsis": "Nova is a cheerful girl who lives in the forest alongside monsters, dreaming of receiving the Blessing of the Earth, known as 'Magia'. However, it seems she has a secret— one only the lord of the forest, Cerberus, knows... \n\nUnaware of this hidden truth, Nova spends her days innocently playing and enjoying life in the forest. Thus begins a wonderful story starring a little girl raised by monsters! \n\n(Source: Magcomi, translated)",
